<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="p.paris;;47" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PParis47</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀπολλώνιος Πτολεμαίωι 

    <lb n="2"/>τῷ πατρὶ χαίρειν. ὀμνύ-

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>ω</corr><sic>ομνυο</sic></choice> τὸν Σάραπιν, <choice><corr>εἰ</corr><sic>ι</sic></choice> μὴ μικρόν 

    <lb n="4"/>τι ἐντρέπομαι, οὐκ ἄν με 

    <lb n="5"/><choice><corr>εἶδες</corr><sic>ιδες</sic></choice> τὸ πρ<add place="supralinear">ό</add>σωπόν μου 

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr>πώποτε</corr><sic>ποποτε</sic></choice>, ὅτι ψεύδηι 

    <lb n="7"/>πάντα καὶ οἱ παρὰ <subst><add place="inline">σὲ</add><del rend="corrected">σοι</del></subst> 

    <lb n="8"/>θεοὶ ὁμοίως, ὅτι ἐν-

    <lb n="9"/>βέβληκαν <choice><corr>ἡμᾶς</corr><sic>υμας</sic></choice> εἰς ὕλην 

    <lb n="10"/><subst><add place="inline">μεγάλην</add><del rend="corrected">μεγαγην</del></subst> καὶ οὗ δυνάμε-

    <lb n="11"/>θα ἀποθανεῖν καὶ <choice><corr>ἐὰν</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">κα<add place="supralinear">ν</add></add><del rend="corrected">κ<del rend="erasure">ια</del></del></subst></sic></choice> ἴδῃς 

    <lb n="12"/>ὅτι μέλλομεν σωθῆναι, 

    <lb n="13"/>τότε <choice><corr>βαπτιζόμεθα</corr><sic>βαπτιζωμεθα</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="14"/>γίνωσ<add place="supralinear">κε</add> ὅτι <choice><corr>πειράσεται</corr><sic>πιρασεται</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="15"/>ὁ δραπέ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied>ης μὴ <choice><corr>ἀφεῖναι</corr><sic>αφιναι</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="16"/>ἡμᾶς ἐπὶ τῶν τόπων 

    <lb n="17"/><choice><corr>εἶναι</corr><sic>ιναι</sic></choice>, χάριν γὰρ ἡμῶν 

    <lb n="18"/><choice><corr>ἐζημίωται</corr><sic>ηζημιοται</sic></choice> εἰς χαλκοῦ 

    <lb n="19"/><expan><ex cert="high">τάλαντα</ex></expan> <num value="15">ιε</num>. ὁ στρατηγὸς ἀνα-

    <lb n="20"/>βαίν<add place="supralinear">ει</add> αὔριον εἰς τὸ Σαραπι-

    <lb n="21"/><choice><corr>εῖον</corr><sic>σαραπιην</sic></choice> καὶ δύο <num value="2"/> ἡμέρας ποι-

    <lb n="22"/>εῖ ἐν τῶι Ἀνουβιείωι 

    <lb n="23"/>πίνων. οὐκ ἔστι ἀνακύ-

    <lb n="24"/>ψα<add place="supralinear">ί με</add> <choice><corr>πώποτε</corr><sic>ποποτε</sic></choice> ἐν τῇ Τρικομίαι 

    <lb n="25"/>ὑπὸ τῆς αἰσχύνης, <choice><corr>εἰ</corr><sic>ι</sic></choice> καὶ 

    <lb n="26"/>αὑτοὺς δεδώκαμεν 

    <lb n="27"/>καὶ ἀποπεπτώκαμεν 

    <lb n="28"/><choice><corr>πλανώμενοι</corr><sic>πλανομενοι</sic></choice> ὑπὸ τῶν 

    <lb n="29"/>θεῶν καὶ πιστεύοντες 

    <lb n="30"/>τὰ ἐνύπνια. εὐτύχει. 
</ab></div><div n="v,ms" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>πρὸ<add place="supralinear">ς</add> τοὺς 

    <lb n="2"/>τὴν ἀλή-

    <lb n="3"/>θειαν λέγοντες. 
</ab></div><div n="v,md" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Πτολεμαί-

    <lb n="2"/>ωι χαίρε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>ν. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.3461" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3461" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notBefore="-0152-09-20" type="textDate">nach 20. Sept. 152 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3461" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. Delekat, Katoche, S. 130.</p></div><div n="meta.3461" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">UPZ</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">70</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">3461</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0245</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">70</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0245;1;70" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3461" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">500</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">287</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.3461" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">P.Par., Planche XXXIV</bibl><bibl type="illustration">Chauveau, L'Égypte au temps de Cléopâtre, V</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.3461" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">P.Par. 47</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Sel. Pap. I 100</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Witkowski, Epistulae privatae 48</bibl></listBibl></div><div n